\newlabel{tab:fairface_clip_fair}{{8}{13}{CLIP ViT-B/32 concept erasure on FairFace (validation HPO for $\lambda $). FairFace provides diverse real-world face images with binary demographic labels (gender, binarized race groups, age). Each method's $\lambda ^*$ is selected from the same grid $\{0.5, 1.0, 2.0, 4.0, 8.0\}$ by lowest validation nonlinear probe accuracy. Controls: 5 least-correlated binary demographic attributes per concept. L/NL Leak: retrained linear / nonlinear probe accuracy (lower = better erasure). $\Delta $Ctrl: mean control accuracy change (closer to zero = more surgical). Embeddings: CLIP ViT-B/32 pooler\_output (768 dimensions)}{table.caption.38}{}}
